{"tid":1531654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[831恐襲] 16人被控暴動罪入面有個係朝鮮籍","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:43:46.000Z","uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8ad5035c186899b9cfc8f77e0ea05a0a7800ab","tid":1531654,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】8月31日灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶衝突，16人被控暴動罪，於西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n <br />\n十六名被告年齡介乎18至42歲，當中有五名學生，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以及一名國籍朝鮮的33歲男子，</span></span></strong><br />\n全部人以暴動罪被起訴。有八人被控於灣仔修頓遊樂場一帶參與暴動，<br />\n七人的暴動罪就涉及銅鑼灣百德新街一帶。 <br />\n另外有一人就被控於銅鑼灣軒尼詩道500號，即希慎廣場一帶參與暴動。<br />\n控方在庭上透露，有三名被告目前仍然留醫<br />\n<br />\n金仔會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a771cc42abb1573810185f0baa7c6fc6161de4","tid":1531654,"uid":232565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"Pray for Kim Kim<br />\n畀人發現外國勢力同幕後精密大佬係佢，不感想像中國會對佢做咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}